{"tid":706314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係搵到新先忘記到舊 定 未忘記到舊唔好搵新","createTime":"2018-06-17T19:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T09:42:00.000Z","uid":176449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcbe2af32992684eed0ff497be8b09c1e1e8a23","tid":706314,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T19:33:55.000Z","msg":"點先忘記到佢<br />\n得閒就諗起佢 發夢又夢見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲朋友叫我搵過個就會忘記佢<br />\n但係又有朋友話我未忘記到佢就搵過個好仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb62648a55742b4f83a605c1c910f178de86570","tid":706314,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T19:34:20.000Z","msg":"好攰"},{"pid":"d02a01850de1da5014b44a8edbbd118df6bed70c","tid":706314,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T19:34:40.000Z","msg":"不斷醒起佢"},{"pid":"2fa77958b3f41de9564fc6a65d5b57f6e9344ce7","tid":706314,"uid":118010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T19:37:01.000Z","msg":"忘記咗先<br />\n未忘記上一個就同第二個一齊 好容易又諗番起上一個 又發現自己可能未放低舊嗰個 到時會傷左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a677613b271681c22ca82b6f9b143b8f7cedb96b","tid":706314,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T20:00:43.000Z","msg":"但係唔搵新係咪難忘記啲"},{"pid":"b10cd8649fd2912f9e95e70e475dec1dde5ea52b","tid":706314,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T21:07:02.000Z","msg":"曾經真心愛過<br />\n就無可能完全忘記到<br />\n人心肉造<br />\n你以為好似機器咁話忘記就忘記？<br />\n忘記唔曬咁係咪唔搵下一個成世單身？"},{"pid":"89dcf692d60a0636d39e370cc75c44dfe26dfd5b","tid":706314,"uid":81168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T21:23:32.000Z","msg":"people replace people"},{"pid":"5bb45d8a5b41e3dc4a98a160e5eb29de1c8aa88e","tid":706314,"uid":118010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"當然忘記係冇可能做到 嗰個人始終喺你人生入面出現過 亦對你有一定影響 <br />\n小弟分享下自己經歷<br />\n我曾經有個好愛嘅女朋友 之後分手 隔左一年左右就同我現任一齊 當時我以為自己ready好 但原來仲會成日諗起前任 加上我間唔中有場合會撞到佢 所以我個心都好矛盾 覺得自己唔係愛現任 而我現任都feel到 我傷害得佢唔少<br />\n<br />\n後來有位朋友就同我講 其實你以為自己未放低 可能你已經放低咗 只係你執著左係放唔放低呢個點 困住咗自己 <br />\n<br />\n聽完我就決定試下唔再睇關前任嘅嘢 但係我係冇unfollow嘅 係要自己習慣性唔故意去睇 後來望到都冇再有特別嘅感覺 可以話 其實時間係可以沖淡一啲嘢 盡量唔睇唔見 其實真係會有一日放低咗而你不自知 俾多啲時間去搵下興趣 提升下自已 好快遇到個更好的<br />\n<br />\nSorry for長篇大論"},{"pid":"d9b1f8d4ab815f7501083da8a75cff9b09eac87e","tid":706314,"uid":83531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"不如話學會去接受你地嘅結局並前進 唔好用忘記嚟逃避"},{"pid":"1f427a2daa430bb81acfa7cd03d8789975fb318e","tid":706314,"uid":164496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b1f8d4ab815f7501083da8a75cff9b09eac87e","tid":706314,"uid":83531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"不如話學會去接受你地嘅結局並前進 唔好用忘記嚟逃避"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:42:00.000Z","msg":"講得好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}